	Fractional increase in chronic respir disease deaths if full distancing*Social distancing affecting chronic disease deaths
	~	dmnl [0,1,0.05]
	~		|

Fractional increase in chronic respir disease deaths if full distancing=
	0.1
	~	dmnl
	~		|

